name: Mookiee
content:
Mookiee, a female wokling, lived on the forest moon of Endor around the time of the Battle of Endor.
Mookiee was one of six 8-inch plush woklings made by Kenner. While the characters of Malani, Nippet, and Wiley were established in the Ewoks television series, Mookiee, Leeni, and Gwig have yet to be identified in a particular source. Mookiee is also featured in the Ewok Woodland Wagon from the Kenner Preschool line.
